@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Habit Tracker";
}

<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>Habit Tracker is a simple yet powerful tool designed to help you build better habits, stay consistent, and achieve your personal goals. Whether you're trying to drink more water, exercise daily, or read every night — this app supports your journey to self-improvement.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🌟 Key Features</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>📅 <strong>Custom Habit Scheduling:</strong> Track habits on specific days (daily, weekdays, weekends, or custom).</li>
        <li>🔥 <strong>Streak Tracking:</strong> Build momentum by maintaining streaks and getting visual feedback on progress.</li>
        <li>📊 <strong>Charts & Insights:</strong> Visualize your progress with bar charts showing your longest and current streaks.</li>
        <li>🔔 <strong>Daily Completion Toggle:</strong> Quickly mark habits as complete with a simple switch.</li>
        <li>💾 <strong>Data Persistence:</strong> All your data is securely saved — no progress lost.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">💡 Why Use Habit Tracker?</h4>
    <p>Research shows that consistent daily actions lead to long-term success. Habit Tracker helps you stay accountable, motivated, and aware of your daily routines.</p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🚀 What's Next?</h4>
    <p>We plan to add notifications, habit-sharing with friends, and more visual insights. Your feedback matters — let us know how we can make this tool even better!</p>

    <p class="text-muted mt-5">Built with 💙 by the Habit Tracker Team</p>
</div>
